article.description: Mason Peatling had 28 points plus 14 rebounds as Eastern Washington got past Montana State 90-84 in the quarterfinals of the Big Sky Conference Tournament on Thursday night. Cody Benzel added 22 points for the Eagles.
article.headline: Peatling lifts EWU to 90-84 win in Big Sky quarterfinal
article.linkText: Peatling lifts EWU to 90-84 win in Big Sky quarterfinal
article.story: BOISE, Idaho -- Mason Peatling had 28 points plus 14 rebounds as Eastern Washington got past Montana State 90-84 in the quarterfinals of the Big Sky Conference Tournament on Thursday night. Cody Benzel added 22 points for the Eagles. Jesse Hunt had 18 points for Eastern Washington (15-17). Keljin Blevins scored a career-high 27 points for the Bobcats (15-17). Tyler Hall added 20 points and seven rebounds. Harald Frey had 12 points. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
